; Remark: This file contains two data sets. The first 
data set was collected at wavelength 0.952 angstrom
and used for refinement of the structure.
The second data set included here was collected at 
wavelength 0.8116 angstrom on a crystal prepared under 
conditions with rubidium substituting for potassium. 
This data set was used to confirm the potassium ion 
binding site.
;
